{"tid":989354,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"占士·米拿被小學老師罰下","createTime":"2019-01-20T19:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T01:49:52.000Z","uid":20634,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"baf907a839e3a935814622416eafd60dddf0709e","tid":989354,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T19:15:30.000Z","msg":"利物浦後衛占士&middot;米拿在本輪英超4-3擊敗水晶宮的比賽中吃到兩張黃牌被罰下場，賽后《迴聲報》披露了一個有趣的事實：將占士&middot;米拿罰下的當值主裁判莫斯(Jon Moss)竟是他的小學老師。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.qunliao.info/fastdfs3/M00/B8/25/ChOxM1xElsGAP6wtAAKcTTADwzI132.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.qunliao.info%2Ffastdfs3%2FM00%2FB8%2F25%2FChOxM1xElsGAP6wtAAKcTTADwzI132.jpg&h=72a0f94a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年占士&middot;米拿就讀於約克郡霍斯福斯的威斯布魯克小學(Westbrook Primary School)時，曾是莫斯的學生，有網友發布了占士&middot;米拿在校隊的合照，圖片中的教練正是莫斯，占士&middot;米拿則擔任隊長。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.qunliao.info/fastdfs3/M00/B8/26/ChOxM1xEmTOATelwAAJMJrgvQK0947.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.qunliao.info%2Ffastdfs3%2FM00%2FB8%2F26%2FChOxM1xEmTOATelwAAJMJrgvQK0947.jpg&h=c1b11f2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.qunliao.info/fastdfs3/M00/B7/6A/ChOxM1xDVOOAVl7fAAtmg499xDc620.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.qunliao.info%2Ffastdfs3%2FM00%2FB7%2F6A%2FChOxM1xDVOOAVl7fAAtmg499xDc620.gif&h=92004892&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來占士&middot;米拿去了霍斯福斯中學，據說他當年是學校的尖子生，通過了11門課程的GCSE(英國中等教育證書)考試，並曾因體育成績出色拿過獎項。<br />\n<br />\n不過，是役占士&middot;米拿的紀律性似乎不太好，他下半場連續兩次對扎哈犯規，莫斯面對昔日的學生掏起黃牌來也是毫不猶豫，《迴聲報》調侃說占士&middot;米拿可能是第一位被自己的小學老師罰下的球員。"},{"pid":"49f8e77f153877c033f7e69122846d69d1cdd648","tid":989354,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T19:16:54.000Z","msg":"reddit d人話最高果行中間係joey barton"},{"pid":"2834ccabeec8df58750c5002f99b23f74ceb6c1d","tid":989354,"uid":165817,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T20:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5xVeq0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5xVeq0.jpg&h=6e1b4e66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大個咗應該幾靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"256d8d99085bac09a47b161511916b09fd0fc7d6","tid":989354,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T21:55:22.000Z","msg":"後衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9865a812f716631e583413b8a197e99f233f4a","tid":989354,"uid":31186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T23:33:36.000Z","msg":"個場比沙夏當狗咁撚"},{"pid":"05dcf1d26ec6046f61e22582b81573d759255b16","tid":989354,"uid":5652,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T23:43:53.000Z","msg":"最衰都係莫斯o拉！"},{"pid":"2919f4b76d6bb1d3bc6f36813c7d4d172d7768fd","tid":989354,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05dcf1d26ec6046f61e22582b81573d759255b16","tid":989354,"uid":5652,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T23:43:53.000Z","msg":"最衰都係莫斯o拉！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T23:45:30.000Z","msg":"費明奴"},{"pid":"54c7abd21bb3009042e6f79c7462f05eb1900b01","tid":989354,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49f8e77f153877c033f7e69122846d69d1cdd648","tid":989354,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T19:16:54.000Z","msg":"reddit d人話最高果行中間係joey barton"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T00:51:50.000Z","msg":"Joey Barton <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c099e035530a24dc3d16ad6b218dd0cd3582fc","tid":989354,"uid":29006,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"05dcf1d26ec6046f61e22582b81573d759255b16","tid":989354,"uid":5652,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"rep